Put the set of keys on the front edge of the blue couch to the right of the cardboard box.

high_descs: Turn around to the table where the plant is.

Turn to the left, go forward, hang a right, go forward, hang a right, go forward, turn to the left where the cardboard box is on the couch.
Put the keys down on the couch in front of the left side of the cardboard box.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left, go forward, hang a left and go to the table where the plant is.
Pick up the set of keys that is on the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right, go forward turn to the left where the cardboard box is on the couch.
Put the keys down on the couch in front of the right side of the cardboard box.
